title: Couples Court Update: K. Lee vs. His Wife In The Case Of The Kitchen Renovation
description:
K. Lee and his wife are currently at odds. Why? Because she wants their kitchen to be renovated. K. Lee knows that it's going to be expensive and doesn't think it's necessary. Who's right, who's wrong?
